*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zrsa16_11.

DATA : gv_a TYPE sy-datum,
       gv_b LIKE gv_a,
       gv_c LIKE gv_a,
       gv_d LIKE gv_a.

*gv_a = sy-datum + 7.
" cal Date (sy-datum)
PERFORM cal_date USING sy-datum '7'
                 CHANGING gv_a.

*gv_b = sy-datum + 14.
PERFORM cal_date2 USING sy-datum '14'
                  CHANGING gv_b.
*gv_c = sy-datum + 21.
PERFORM cal_date3 USING sy-datum '21'
                  CHANGING gv_c.
*gv_d = sy-datum + 28.
PERFORM cal_date4 USING sy-datum '28'
                  CHANGING gv_d.


PERFORM display_info.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form cal_date
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM cal_date USING VALUE(p_date)
                    VALUE(p_days)
              CHANGING VALUE(p_new_date).
p_new_date = p_date + p_days.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form cal_date2
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM cal_date2 USING VALUE(p_date)
                     VALUE(p_days)
               CHANGING VALUE(p_new_date).
p_new_date = p_date + p_days.
ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form cal_date3
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> SY_DATUM
*&      --> P_
*&      <-- GV_C
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM cal_date3  USING VALUE(p_date)
                      VALUE(p_days)
                CHANGING VALUE(p_new_date).
  p_new_date = p_date + p_days.

ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form cal_date4
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&      --> SY_DATUM
*&      --> P_
*&      <-- GV_D
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM cal_date4  USING VALUE(p_date)
                      VALUE(p_days)
                CHANGING VALUE(p_new_date).
  p_new_date = p_date + p_days.

ENDFORM.
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form display_info
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& -->  p1        text
*& <--  p2        text
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM display_info .
  WRITE: gv_a, gv_b, gv_c, gv_d.
ENDFORM.
